  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cook
    A cook that can make pizza in some amount of time.
    Delivery

    Event representation to store in logs.
    Manager
    Class that controls the cooking cycle.
    Orders
    Pool of orders that no one has started cooking.
    Store
    Storage for orders while they are cooked but not started delivering.
